# Style Guide: Manga Bot Game Frontend

## Visual Theme
- **Overall aesthetic:** Japanese manga panel style.
- **Backgrounds:** Curtain-texture patterns, bold contrasts (black/white with splashes of red or pastel).
- **Characters:** 
  - Red-haired, pale-skinned girl with slim mouth.
  - User-inspired avatar (placeholder image).
- **UI Elements:** 
  - Buttons styled like manga speech bubbles with thick outlines.
  - Speed lines and panel effects for animations.
- **Fonts:** Use manga-inspired fonts (handwritten or bold comic styles).
- **Colors (psychological cues):**
  - Buy-green: #28a745
  - Alert-red: #dc3545
  - Info-blue: #007bff
  - Neutral-gray: #6c757d

## Audio
- **Primary sound effect:** "chin chin" (small bell-like chime).
- **Usage:** Play on button clicks, wallet connect, character selection.
- **Optional effects:** "ding" or "level up" sounds for successful actions.
- **Volume:** Subtle, not intrusive; user should be able to toggle sounds.

## UX / Interaction
- **Character Selection:** 
  - Avatars displayed with manga-style frames.
  - Selection triggers sound + highlight effect.
- **Wallet Connect:** 
  - Button styled as a manga power-up bubble.
  - Status displayed in manga narrator text.
- **Demo Button:** 
  - Animates character "jumping" into wallet with speed lines.
- **Disclaimer:** 
  - Persistent at bottom of page.
  - Styled like a manga narrator box (black outline, white fill).
  - Text: "This is for entertainment only. Human behavior experimental project."

## Layout
- **Home Page:** 
  - Title styled like manga panel text.
  - CharacterSelect, WalletConnect, DemoButton, DisclaimerBox.
- **Game Page:** 
  - Shows chosen character interacting with wallet.
  - Manga-style "LEVEL UP" text when bot is installed.
  - Use MangaButton for actions.

## Rules
- Always keep disclaimer visible.
- All buttons must trigger sound effects.
- Animations should use manga tropes (speed lines, panel transitions).
- Colors must follow psychological cues strictly.
- Keep components modular and reusable.
